{"tid":2491794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人今晚響尖沙咀畀人捉住影相？","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:47:26.000Z","uid":67518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d615f01f0f36d4fddb2fc24c064753962a393463","tid":2491794,"uid":67518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"同朋友食完飯響條街吹水，突然有中年女人走埋嚟話要影相，我初頭以為係幫佢哋揸機影，就話好，點知係同我哋影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n果下真係反應唔切而冇拒絕到，就畀佢哋捉住影咗張相，又話咩做啲正能量嘅事，另外都有個朋友畀佢哋影咗。<br />\n<br />\n之後諗返越諗越奇怪，唔知佢哋影嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾咁啱又有朋友經過尖沙咀，都遇到有班人係咁捉住人影相。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知究竟咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7132c0fa72924b14b202db518f31fc3aa6f555b0","tid":2491794,"uid":67518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"458c183a1c4c4be66067e41a4f037331586aeeec","tid":2491794,"uid":254453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"拍youtube?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c7864fcfc316f3b949accfee93561dcbc3b458","tid":2491794,"uid":67518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458c183a1c4c4be66067e41a4f037331586aeeec","tid":2491794,"uid":254453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"拍youtube?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但剩係見到佢哋影相，唔覺有人拍緊片，仲要捉人影相嘅都係中年人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bf53d6d6991ec58d5a7397a903326cdd15e78d","tid":2491794,"uid":51794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,